snippet.title: Rose and Locket - Official Demo Release Trailer | The MIX x Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Get another look at the world of Rose and Locket in this trailer for the upcoming action-platformer adventure game. Join Rose, a gunslinging mother fueled by devotion and vengeance, on a journey to free her daughter's soul from a mysterious silver locket. Master powerful weapons and abilities as you battle through the colorful world of the Underwest, depicted by hand-drawn animation inspired by the works of Genndy Tartakovsky. A demo for Rose and Locket is available now on Steam.
